'''生命科学突破奖'''（{{lang-en|Breakthrough Prize in Life Sciences}}）是[[突破奖|突破奖]]其中一項，由[[Google|Google]]联合创辦人[[謝爾蓋·布林|謝爾蓋·布林]]、[[23andMe|23andMe]]联合创辦人[[安妮·沃西基|安妮·沃西基]]、[[社交媒體|社交媒體]][[Facebook|Facebook]]创辦人[[马克·扎克伯格|马克·扎克伯格]]及其妻[[普莉希拉·陳|普莉希拉·陳]]、和[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]企業家[[尤里·米尔纳|尤里·米尔纳]]創立，用以奖励对治疗顽疾和延长[[人类|人类]]寿命有杰出貢獻的研究者<ref>{{cite news |author1=Carroll, Rory |title=Breakthrough Prize announced by Silicon Valley entrepreneurs |url=https://www.theguardian.com/science/2013/feb/20/breakthrough-prize-silicon-valley-entrepreneurs |accessdate=2022-04-15 |work=[[衛報|衛報]] |date=2013-02-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415075733/https://www.theguardian.com/science/2013/feb/20/breakthrough-prize-silicon-valley-entrepreneurs |archivedate=2022-04-15 |language=en}}</ref>，每年最少一位得獎者會因[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]或[[神經退化障礙|神經退化性疾病]]相關研究而獲獎<ref>{{cite web |title=Rules |url=https://breakthroughprize.org/Rules/2 |publisher=[[突破獎|突破獎基金會]] |accessdate=2022-04-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20220415080541/https://breakthroughprize.org/Rules/2 |archivedate=2022-04-15 |language=en}}</ref>。生命科学突破奖于2013年开始颁发，每一位獲獎者都可獨得獎金300萬[[美元|美元]]奖金，是迄今奖金最高的[[生物學|生物學]]或[[醫學|醫學]]奖项<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/8ba327a8-7b7e-11e2-95b9-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2yacUqM3Z |title=Winners of life science prize revealed |work=[[金融時報|金融時報]] |accessdate=2015-11-19 |archive-date=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141207145519/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/8ba327a8-7b7e-11e2-95b9-00144feabdc0.html#axzz2yacUqM3Z}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Take that, Alfred |url=http://www.economist.com/blogs/babbage/2013/02/science-prizes |work=[[經濟學人|經濟學人]] |date=2013-02-20 |accessdate=2015-02-13 |archive-date=2017-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107060652/https://www.economist.com/blogs/babbage/2013/02/science-prizes |language=en}}</ref>。






